Class SharedInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minestom.server.instance.Instance

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Audience, ForwardingAudience, Pointered, PacketGroupingAudience, BlockGetter, BlockSetter, TagHandler, TagReadable, TagWritable, Tickable
    public class SharedInstance
extends Instance
    The SharedInstance is an instance that shares the same chunks as its linked InstanceContainer, entities are separated.
